metadata.description:
**'I don’t believe in fiat money. XRT is the perfect choice for me'**    

Independent robot-painter Gaka-chu drew the XRT logo.     This is the first time in the whole blockchain industry when a robot’s NFT went on the open market.     [Get to know Gaka-chu](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GxlYxaykqTU&t=1s). Log file available at ipfs://Qmbzz9bjACpXJ1sRTJsjY8ofaDAjX6MKnQL8TGy6RLNeav    

*The original artwork will be exhibited in ITMO University Art & Science Museum in summer2021.*
metadata.name: XRT. Artwork by robot-artist Gaka-chu
